cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and specifically focuses on improving temporal relation extraction. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses probabilistic models and statistical analysis, which suggests that it could also fit into categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval and data mining techniques, which could place it in categories such as cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
